# ksw TUI demo — fuzzy search, navigate, switch
Output demo/tui.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 800
Set Height 420
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8

Env KUBECONFIG demo/kubeconfig-demo.yaml

Type "ksw"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1500ms

Type "pay"
Sleep 800ms

Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms

Enter
Sleep 1200ms
